[An official confirmation, including details on clinical and diagnostic aspects of the case, are anticipated.

For a map showing the distribution of SBV as updated 20 Jul 2012 (just prior to the addition of Switzerland), see http://www.flutrackers.com/forum/attachment.php?attachmentid=15054&d=1342182811. The virus (or rather infected vectors) may have spread to Switzerland from France or Germany.

Further updated information on the current SBV situation in Switzerland, in the other 9 infected countries, and throughout the rest of Europe may become clearer if/when a serosurvey is applied.

For a map showing the location of the Jura canton, see http://tinyurl.com/cyg3svm. - Mod.AS

